  "informal_statement": "For every natural number n, n! > 0 (the factorial of n is positive).",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Induction on n. Base case n = 0: 0! = 1 > 0 by definition. Successor case: given ih : k! > 0, rewrite (k+1)! via Nat.factorial_succ to (k+1) * k!, then Nat.mul_pos closes it from (k+1) > 0 and ih.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem factorial_pos_induction (n : ℕ) : 0 < Nat.factorial n",
